      review:
        "There are no coincidences. If you're right here and Right Now reading this, there's a reason, a logical cause; but not always a clear first principle or motiff. That's when Art can give us a little push. Haibane Renmei is a very earthy, soft anime with an ethereal touch. The settings, characters, pace, and the (beautiful) music transport you and made feel the love present in the every day unimportant things of life and the world. Sure, their \"handmade\" craftsmanship is shown. Different people have different tastes, and we all have different needs. I have experienced how work's like this can have a profound effect on thedeep consciousness or psyche, meanwhile others (some friends as example), can simple pass on that, like was nothing. The world is a mysterious place, and the most mysterious of their corners is the human hearth.\n\nIf you're lucky enough, like I am, this show will change something inside of you for the better. That's all.",
