      review:
        "Oh well I randomly decided to do this on a whim because this anime had a profound effect on me. As in, it actually made me think about the stuff that is happening, why its happening, who is responsible etc. I really have a soft spot for anime that make me question why I'm even watching them in the first place (Like Serial experiments Lain aswell) Maybe most of you have seen it already, Maybe most of you havent even heard about it but regardless it has quite a bit of historical value in that it actually had a really bold ending which I wont spoil obviouslylmao.\n\nStory :(5)\nJust your run of the mill harem romance school story, Below average actually.\n\nCharacters :(5)\nThe characters are well... Extremely selfish and maybe life like? Idk how to describe it but I hated almost all the characters near the end and imo that speaks volumes about the writing atleast. \n\nAnimation :(5)\nExtremely average\n\nMusic :(8)\nNow this is where the anime somewhat excels , Had some really good songs here and there and the way they used them was nice.\n\nEnjoyment:(8)\nNow you're probably thinking why would I rate this an 8 because its average rating is somewhere around 5.5 something.\nI rate an anime based on, beginning, music, how many times it made me question stuff, or had some impact or some moments which I might not forget and lastly the ending and boy does this have one of the most satisfying endings I've seen in anime recently. \n\nIf anyone has seen it dont spoil in the comments because its one of those anime where you should go completely blind and see for yourself.\nDo not google it or anything, Just start watching\n\nIf you read all that, Thanks!\nHere's a cookie 🍪",
