      date: "2023-08-01T00:42:00+00:00",
      review:
        "Yandare warning & dub con (Uke consents but then keeps saying stop, slow down and stop so dub con incase anyone doesn't want to read a story with that) Their second time the uke fully consents and even begs for it, those warnings aside the story is good for a Yandare story, unlike most Yandare stories this one has the Seme give the uke space so the uke can realize he loves the Seme which is very different from most Yandare stories where the Yandare just force themselves regardless of everything. Over all the story revolves around the uke figuring out his feelings towards the seme(the Yandare character) after the Yandare character confesses. Then we see the Yandare and how he has worked to make the uke fall for him. It's hard to say who the MC and ML is because it starts off with the Uke's point of view but then other chapters it's the Semes point of view so they are both the ML &amp; the MC, that is why I just refered to them as Uke &amp; Seme because otherwise it could confuse people. The Smut scenes were hot especially their 2nd time (with the exception of their first time since it was dubcon - that one as well as the ending is what made me rate this a 8 instead of 10)\n\nThis isn't for those who want something cute and fluffy but definitely a really good Yandare story for those who do like the genre. The ending though was abrupt, it felt like it was going to get a second volume however from what I know it doesn't have one. Really hope the author continues this story because it's definitely good with nice art!",
